            <p>Fuel oil procured from non-reliable sources often has high levels of water and solids. Stored fuel oil also accumulates water and rust contaminants. <a href="/alfa-laval-centrifugal-separator/">Alfa Laval centrifugal separators</a> purify the fuel oil to remove sludge and water, delivering engine-ready HFO for reliable performance.</p>
            <p>The system shown includes an <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Alfa Laval disc stack centrifuge</a> with accessories — in-line electric heaters and high-pressure pumps to ease the use of HFO instead of diesel. The operational cost savings by switching fuels justified the cost of the centrifuge system.</p>
