            <p>Lubricating oil is the lifeline of a power plant engine or turbine. Condensation and bearing wear particles are the primary impurities in all lube oils.</p>
            <p>Contaminated lube oil leads to premature equipment failure, unanticipated downtime, and unplanned maintenance. Lube oil conditioning modules maintain moisture and particle contamination to an acceptable level. This clean lube oil reduces downtime and improves equipment reliability.</p>
